                     <interp inst="t18300916-155-off808" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               inciting, procuring, aiding, and counciling the said John Wormersley to do and commit the said felony
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>2nd COUNT, calling the instrument a letter of attorney.</p>
               <p>3rd and 4th COUNTS, like the first and second, only stating the intent to be to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-155-victim1346" type="victimName">
                     Ann 
                     Wallis
                  <interp inst="t18300916-155-victim1346" type="surname" value="Wallis"></interp>
